divs: Sighting DetailsI woke up at 2 o'clock in the morning, then I saw two lights on the sky. I first realize the two lights as helicopters, but when I looked at them a few moments, i couldn't exactly define it as human objects. Later, I tried to identify which object they could be. When I looked at them closer, they blinked in an evenly way. I wanted to record the objects with a camera, but at first I didn't know exactly, if there are UFO's. In the end it was too late. They flew away and leaved a bright glimming veil on the sky. I didn't actually knot, if there were unknowing flying objects at all, but one thing I can say. If there weren't human produced flying objects, what else they can actually be?...
Summary: Two undefinable lights on the sky
